TODOS:

Although Genix is already able to generate good-quality 
annotations for a wide variety of microbial genomes, we
are constantly working to include new features and fix
some issues. Here we describe some of the thinks we want
to add in future releases ^^

- Gene finding based on multiple programs.
- Faster protein identification.
- Better identification of frameshifted genes.
- Add the COG database (RPS-BLAST+).
- Add support to BLAST2GO (BLAST2G0 CLI).
- Add support to Interproscan.
